title: FF 01-16 (2012-2014, Dgtl, TheGroup + Zone-E)
description: Matt Fraction's glorious, loopy, hilarious, time-twisting run on FF and Fantastic Four comes to a close! While the Reed, Sue, Johnny, and Ben are in the future, Scott Lang and the Future Foundation gang square off against the present Doctor Doom! Will Scott be able to overcome his fears and defeat the Doctor? Will the kids use their powers as a group to blast the doombots? Do Carla, Jennifer, and Medusa (along with Dragon Man) have what it takes to save the future? Find out in this brilliant run which contains the final issue! I have used a lot of exclamation and question marks and I can't stop! Please seed and enjoy! :-)
